  "response": "Yes, boys can experience being \"friendzoned,\" a term that generally refers to a situation where one person has romantic feelings for another who does not reciprocate those feelings and prefers to keep the relationship platonic. This can happen to anyone, regardless of gender. The dynamics of attraction and friendship can be complex, and both boys and girls may find themselves in similar situations based on their feelings and the feelings of their friends.",
